        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "We will also need to include metrics for reporting success, fail and error outcomes to a dash."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Acceptance Criteria",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "strong"
            },
            {
              "type": "underline"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Given a NC lead provider"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When they are a supporting smart bidding "
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "And they send us a response about a lead we’ve bid on"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Then we should successfully receive that bid via this new endpoint"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "AC for reporting outcomes and failures. Add in traces"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

